HEADWORD: Tigella
<hw>Ti*gel"la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., from F.
<ets>tige</ets> stem or stock.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>That part
